    <h3 itemprop="headline">Why security matters in the meeting room</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      For years, meeting room technology was evaluated primarily on ease of use and audiovisual quality. If people could walk in, plug in, and start presenting, the job was considered done. That mindset no longer holds.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/28/why-security-matters-in-the-meeting-room/"  >(Computer World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
