    <h3 itemprop="headline">The AP Interview: Ukraine bets on battlefield AI as the race for weapons autonomy intensifies</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Ukraine is accelerating the use of artificial intelligence to retain an edge on the battlefield, as the war with Russia enters a new technological phase.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/30/the-ap-interview-ukraine-bets-on-battlefield-ai-as-the-race-for-weapons-autonomy-intensifies/"  >(Derek Gatopoulos And Hanna Arhirova, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
